Creating a string in java by using these two method 
1. Using String literal :
String s = “GeeksforGeeks”;
2. Using new keyword :
String s = new String (“GeeksforGeeks”);



String Reverse..
public class Main
{
	public static void main(String[] args) {
	    String str1 = "bharath";
	  for(int i=str1.length()-1;i>=0;i--){
	      char ch = str1.charAt(i);       //get Character of the String
	      String ch1 = Character.toString(ch);     //change the Character into String
	      System.out.print(ch1);
	  }
	}
}
